    "body": "I started sketching out the container side of an allocator API before hitting #8059. With an implementation of vectors and unique pointers taking an allocator type parameter and an allocator instance via a `with_alloc` constructor, it's easy to build any other containers like trees or hash tables on top of them with allocator parameters too.\n\nhttps://github.com/thestinger/rust-core/blob/master/core/vec.rs\n",
